cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS

This paper deals with natural language processing and statistical analysis of text data, which are common topics in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the use of multi-word phrases suggests a focus on language modeling and potentially even text generation, which could fall under the sub-category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
